text:
The reason it's important
to have a robust data strategy
for generative AI success is
that it drives our ongoing improvement

and innovation from one
product to the next as we seek
to provide better products

and better experiences for our
customers and their patients.
AWS has been critical in ensuring
that our data is high quality and secured
and governed properly.

There is a minimum level
that you can expect from AWS
for a company that deals in PHI.

Even as a high trust
certified company, we know

that AWS is always a very
good steward of our data
and is there to make sure
that we're doing the correct things With PHI.

Now we have a one-stop
shop where we can do all
of our core development

and we can access a variety
of different, very powerful

and very capable generative AI
models all in the same place.
And we have the expertise

and the support of the
AWS Generative AI team.
